    • scrapeWebsite

      public org.jsoup.select.Elements scrapeWebsite(String searchURL, String elementCSSClasses) throws Exception
      Scrapes given website and returns web elements. In our case it returns an html element with either car brands or cars list.
      Parameters:
      searchURL - website search URL
      elementCSSClasses - used as car brand or cars list html elements identifier
      Returns:
      htmlElements scraped html elements
      Throws:
